ng\"**: 表示拨号时遇到了传输错误\n- **\"checkoutservice\"**: 执行失败的服务\n\n### Hypotheses\n1. **Component**: \"checkoutservice\"\n   - **Reason**: \"connection refused\" 到目标IP和端口导致拨号错误\n   - **Evidence**: \n     ```\n     \"failed to send order confirmation to \\\"someone@example.com\\\": rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.49.244:5000: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\n     ```\n\n### JSON 输出格式\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"connection refused\", \"transport: Error while dialing\", \"checkoutservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"connection refused to dial tcp 10.233.49.244:5000 resulting in transport error\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to send order confirmation to \\\"someone@example.com\\\": rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.49.244:5000: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n从日志中可见 `checkoutservice` 出现了连接拒绝错误，且问题发生时刻与给定的异常检测时间范围匹配。请注意，这个问题可能涉及网络配置，如防火墙或服务发现机制未正确配置。进一步的调查可能需要检查 `checkoutservice` 和目标服务之间的网络路径配置。", "metric_analysis_findings": "已成功加载故障期间的指标数据，并发现以下异常调用链：\n\n### 异常指标\n- `client_error_ratio` (cartservice, cartservice-0)\n- `error_ratio` (cartservice, cartservice-0)\n- `rrt_max` (emailservice, emailservice-0)\n- `rrt_max` (emailservice, emailservice-1)\n- `rrt_max` (emailservice, emailservice-2)\n- `rrt_max` (shippingservice, shippingservice-1)\n- `rrt_max` (paymentservice, paymentservice-2)\n- `io_util` (tidb-tikv)\n- `node_cpu_usage_rate` (aiops-k8s-03)\n- `node_memory_usage_rate` (aiops-k8s-04)\n- `node_memory_usage_rate` (aiops-k8s-05)\n\n### 异常实体发现\n1. **Cartservice-0**\n   - **异常原因**: `client_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 的故障 P99 值显著上升到 19.29，`median_change_ratio` 达到 2.0。\n   - **关联节点**: aiops-k8s-03\n   - **可能根因**: 服务故障导致错误比例激增。\n\n2. **Emailservice Pods**\n   - **异常原因**: 多个 Pod 中的 `rrt_max` 显著上升，其中 `emailservice-0` 的 P99 从 6582.8 增加到 61502.0，变化比例达到 1.6133。\n   - **可能根因**: 邮件服务相关的性能问题导致响应时间大幅增加。\n\n3. **Shippingservice-1**\n   - **异常原因**: `rrt_max` 的变化比例达到 1.2621。\n   - **可能根因**: 运输服务响应速度减慢。\n\n4. **Tidb-tikv**\n   - **异常原因**: `io_util` 的 P99 变化比例达到 0.664，暗示数据库 IO 系统压力增加。\n   - **可能根因**: 数据库组件 IO 利用率过高可能导致系统响应延迟。\n\n5. **节点 aiops-k8s-03**\n   - **异常原因**: `node_cpu_usage_rate` 在故障期间的 P99 变化比例达到 0.5163，可能表明整体负载增加。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"io_util\",\n    \"node_cpu_usage_rate\",\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"The error ratio increased significantly with fault P99 at 19.29, indicating issues within service operations.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio, error_ratio changes with high ratios during the fault.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Rapid increase in rrt_max across multiple emailservice pods, indicating performance degradation in email response times.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Significant rrt_max spike observed in emailservice-0 with fault P99 at 61502.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased latency in shippingservice-1, impacting responsiveness.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Higher rrt_max values noted.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"IO utilization spiked, potentially causing delays.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Increased io_util observed during the fault period.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node CPU usage rate increase indicates overall load issue.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Higher node_cpu_usage_rate during the critical timeframe.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
